stateDiagram-v2
    %% ── POS SALE lifecycle ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
    [*] --> PENDING_PAYMENT : POS cashier confirms payment\n(order INSERT)
    PENDING_PAYMENT --> CONFIRMED : UPDATE status\n→ guard_stock_on_confirm (BEFORE)\n→ deduct_stock_on_confirm (AFTER)\n→ batch quantities decremented

    %% ── Marketplace / WhatsApp order lifecycle ──────────────────────────────
    [*] --> DRAFT : Customer creates order\n(SALES_ORDER or marketplace)
    DRAFT --> PENDING_PAYMENT : Customer proceeds to checkout
    PENDING_PAYMENT --> PAYMENT_VERIFYING : Online payment selected
    PAYMENT_VERIFYING --> CONFIRMED : Payment verified
    PENDING_PAYMENT --> CONFIRMED : Cash payment

    %% ── Sales Order specific states ─────────────────────────────────────────
    DRAFT --> PARTIALLY_FULFILLED : First Sales Invoice created\n(some lines still unfulfilled)
    PARTIALLY_FULFILLED --> PARTIALLY_FULFILLED : Another Sales Invoice created\n(more lines invoiced)
    PARTIALLY_FULFILLED --> CONFIRMED : All lines fully invoiced

    %% ── SALES_INVOICE / PURCHASE_INVOICE: inserted directly at CONFIRMED ────
    note right of CONFIRMED
        SALES_INVOICE and PURCHASE_INVOICE
        are INSERT'd directly at CONFIRMED.
        deduct_stock / restock triggers fire
        on AFTER INSERT (migration 062).
    end note

    %% ── Fulfilment flow ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    CONFIRMED --> PROCESSING : Staff begins fulfilment
    PROCESSING --> DISPATCHED : Handed to rider\n(pickup OTP sent to vendor)
    DISPATCHED --> DELIVERED : Customer received\n(delivery OTP verified)
    DELIVERED --> COMPLETED : Sale finalized

    %% ── Cancellations ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    DRAFT --> CANCELLED : Cancelled before payment
    PENDING_PAYMENT --> CANCELLED : Payment failed or staff cancels
    PAYMENT_VERIFYING --> CANCELLED : Verification failed
    CONFIRMED --> CANCELLED : Staff cancels\n→ stock restored (RETURN movements)
    PROCESSING --> CANCELLED : Staff cancels\n→ stock restored
    DISPATCHED --> CANCELLATION_REQUESTED : Customer requests
    CANCELLATION_REQUESTED --> CANCELLED : Approved\n→ stock restored

    %% ── Refunds ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    CONFIRMED --> REFUND_REQUESTED : Manager requests refund
    DELIVERED --> REFUND_REQUESTED : Manager requests refund
    COMPLETED --> REFUND_REQUESTED : Manager requests refund
    REFUND_REQUESTED --> REFUND_APPROVED : Manager approves
    REFUND_REQUESTED --> REFUND_REJECTED : Manager rejects
    REFUND_APPROVED --> REFUND_PROCESSING : Processing refund
    REFUND_PROCESSING --> REFUNDED : Complete\n→ stock restored (RETURN movements)

    %% ── Replacements ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    CONFIRMED --> REPLACEMENT_REQUESTED : Customer requests replacement
    DELIVERED --> REPLACEMENT_REQUESTED : Customer requests replacement
    COMPLETED --> REPLACEMENT_REQUESTED : Customer requests replacement
    REPLACEMENT_REQUESTED --> REPLACEMENT_APPROVED : Approved
    REPLACEMENT_APPROVED --> REPLACEMENT_SHIPPED : Shipped
    REPLACEMENT_SHIPPED --> REPLACEMENT_DELIVERED : Delivered

    %% ── Terminal states ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    CANCELLED --> [*]
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    REFUNDED --> [*]
    REFUND_REJECTED --> [*]
    REPLACEMENT_DELIVERED --> [*]
